I"B<h2 id="ingredients">Ingredients</h2>

<ol>
  <li>A burger bun</li>
  <li>A fat burder patty</li>
  <li>Any kind of toppings</li>
</ol>

<h2 id="steps">Steps</h2>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p>Start frying your patty in oil or butter</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Reduce the Heat as the patty starts to sizzle</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Put your burger buns in a toaster</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Wait until the patty is clearly cooked</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Retrieve the bun and the patty</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Put the patty on the bun and add any toppings you want</p>
  </li>
</ol>

